---
const clients = [
  { name: "WhatsMojo", logo: "/images/clients/mojo-logo.png" },
  { name: "Toothpaste Drops", logo: "/images/clients/drops-logo-black.png" },
  { name: "CAPULET", logo: "/images/clients/capulet.logo.avif" },
  { name: "Hummingbird", logo: "/images/clients/hummingbird.png" },
  { name: "Evercleaner", logo: "/images/clients/evercleaner-logo_new.svg" },
  { name: "Blitz", logo: "/images/clients/blitz.svg" },
  { name: "Hello Hairless", logo: "/images/clients/hello-hairless-logo.svg" },
];
---

<section id="clients" class="clients">
  <div class="clients-container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="clients-header">
      <div class="header-left">
        <div class="header-label">
          <span class="label-number">07</span>
          <span class="label-text">Kunden</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="clients-title">
          Vertraut von ambitionierten
          <span class="title-accent">Marken</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
    </header>
  </div>

  <!-- Logo Ticker - Full Width -->
  <div class="ticker-wrapper">
    <div class="ticker">
      <div class="ticker-track">
        {/* First set */}
        {clients.map((client) => (
          <div class="client-item">
            <img src={client.logo} alt={client.name} class="client-logo" />
          </div>
        ))}
        {/* Duplicate for seamless loop */}
        {clients.map((client) => (
          <div class="client-item">
            <img src={client.logo} alt={client.name} class="client-logo" />
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="clients-container">
    <!-- Testimonial -->
    <div class="testimonial">
      <blockquote class="testimonial-quote">
        „Fabian hat unsere gesamte Leadgenerierungs-Plattform von Grund auf gebaut. Sauberer Code, schnelle Lieferung, und er hat wirklich verstanden, was wir für unsere Growth-Marketing-Kunden brauchen."
      </blockquote>
      <div class="testimonial-author">
        <span class="author-name">Blitz Growth</span>
        <span class="author-role">Performance Marketing Agentur</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .clients {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: clamp(5rem, 12vw, 8rem) 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .clients-container {
    max-width: 1800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  }

  /* Header */
  .clients-header {
    margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    padding-bottom: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .header-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .label-number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #a7a9ac;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .label-text {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #0c0c0c;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .clients-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0c0c0c;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .title-accent {
    color: #0c0c0c;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .title-accent::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0.05em;
    left: -0.1em;
    right: -0.1em;
    height: 0.35em;
    background-color: #00FF9C;
    -webkit-mask: url('/brush-stroke.png') center/100% 100% no-repeat;
    mask: url('/brush-stroke.png') center/100% 100% no-repeat;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  /* Ticker */
  .ticker-wrapper {
    margin-bottom: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    position: relative;
  }

  .ticker-wrapper::before,
  .ticker-wrapper::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100px;
    z-index: 2;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ticker-wrapper::before {
    left: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, transparent);
  }

  .ticker-wrapper::after {
    right: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to left, #ffffff, transparent);
  }

  .ticker {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ticker-track {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    animation: ticker 40s linear infinite;
  }

  .ticker:hover .ticker-track {
    animation-play-state: paused;
  }

  @keyframes ticker {
    0% {
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }
  }

  .client-item {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding: 0 clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
    transition: opacity 0.3s var(--ease-out-quart);
  }

  a.client-item:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .client-logo {
    height: 20px;
    width: auto;
    max-width: 120px;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: grayscale(100%);
    opacity: 0.6;
    transition: all 0.3s var(--ease-out-quart);
  }

  .client-item:hover .client-logo {
    filter: grayscale(0%);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* Testimonial */
  .testimonial {
    max-width: 800px;
    padding-top: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .testimonial-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2vw, 1.375rem);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
  }

  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .author-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #0c0c0c;
  }

  .author-role {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #a7a9ac;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .ticker-wrapper::before,
    .ticker-wrapper::after {
      width: 40px;
    }
  }

  /* Reduce motion for accessibility */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .ticker-track {
      animation: none;
    }
  }
</style>
